uthors/nyadidi"><meta name="description" content="Democrat Kamala Harris is a California senator running for president."><meta name="dateCreated" content="2019-02-15T19:54:50.936905Z"><meta name="datePublished" content="2019-02-15T19:54:50.936905Z"><meta name="dateModified" content="2019-12-03T18:25:49.076000Z"><meta name="articleBody" content="&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Editor&amp;#x27;s Note&lt;/strong&gt;: Harris&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;dropped out&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-drops-out-2020-campaign-50c45cbe-e917-4004-996c-1096b2a61a80.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-drops-out-2020-campaign-50c45cbe-e917-4004-996c-1096b2a61a80.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;dropped out&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;of the race on December 3rd, 2019. Below is our original article on her candidacy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Democrat Kamala Harris is a California senator who took office at the start of Trump&amp;#x27;s presidency and became one of the most vocal foils for Trump&amp;#x27;s political nominees during heated questioning in confirmation hearings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Key facts:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Current position: &lt;/strong&gt;California senator — 2 years served&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Age: &lt;/strong&gt;54&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Born: &lt;/strong&gt;Oakland&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Undergraduate&lt;/strong&gt;: Howard University&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date candidacy announced: &lt;/strong&gt;Jan. 21, 2019&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;% of votes in line with Trump, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;per FiveThirtyEight&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;per FiveThirtyEight&lt;/a&gt;: 17.0%&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous roles: &lt;/strong&gt;California attorney general (2011-2017); San Francisco district attorney (2004-2011); prosecutor&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Stance on key issues:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Green New Deal&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Co-sponsor&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-green-new-deal-d0103689-3b72-4c6c-8018-cc8b18950476.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-green-new-deal-d0103689-3b72-4c6c-8018-cc8b18950476.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Co-sponsor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Medicare for All&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Co-sponsored Sen. Bernie Sanders&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-kamala-harris-medicare-for-all-d3598f7e-d492-4d45-9dc4-7a58c908556d.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-kamala-harris-medicare-for-all-d3598f7e-d492-4d45-9dc4-7a58c908556d.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Co-sponsored Sen. Bernie Sanders&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#x27; bill.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drug prices:&lt;/strong&gt; Would allow the Department of Health and Human Services to determine a &amp;quot;fair price&amp;quot; for drugs meeting certain conditions, per the &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Washington Post&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/kamala-harris-announces-plan-on-drug-prices-as-democratic-health-care-debate-intensifies/2019/07/15/a2d378a2-a731-11e9-9214-246e594de5d5_story.html?utm_term=.8cad6e7d6512&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/kamala-harris-announces-plan-on-drug-prices-as-democratic-health-care-debate-intensifies/2019/07/15/a2d378a2-a731-11e9-9214-246e594de5d5_story.html?utm_term=.8cad6e7d6512&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marijuana legalization: &lt;/strong&gt;Proposed&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot; federal legalization of marijuana&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-marijuana-2020-presidential-election-746539ba-edad-457f-8790-16675d628d9f.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-marijuana-2020-presidential-election-746539ba-edad-457f-8790-16675d628d9f.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt; federal legalization of marijuana&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teacher pay: &lt;/strong&gt;Has&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot; a plan to give the average teacher a $13,500 salary increase&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-teacher-pay-plan-7d7cc1e6-a157-4f5a-9117-8a6b60e3f8b8.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-teacher-pay-plan-7d7cc1e6-a157-4f5a-9117-8a6b60e3f8b8.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt; a plan to give the average teacher a $13,500 salary increase&lt;/a&gt;, costing an estimated $315 billion over 10 years.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Taxes: &lt;/strong&gt;Introduced the LIFT the Middle Class Act, which &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Vox&amp;#x27;s Dylan Matthews explained&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.vox.com/future-perfect/2018/10/19/17995374/kamala-harris-lift-act-basic-income-cash-eitc&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.vox.com/future-perfect/2018/10/19/17995374/kamala-harris-lift-act-basic-income-cash-eitc&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Vox&amp;#x27;s Dylan Matthews explained&lt;/a&gt; as an expansion of the earned income tax credit. She also proposed offering tax credits to help people pay rent.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;In May, said she&amp;#x27;d &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;fully repeal the 2017 Republican tax law&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-trump-tax-law-lift-act-b6cd009c-5ce2-42de-8d3d-4b62289531c8.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-trump-tax-law-lift-act-b6cd009c-5ce2-42de-8d3d-4b62289531c8.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;fully repeal the 2017 Republican tax law&lt;/a&gt; and replace it with LIFT.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abortion: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Proposed&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-abortion-plan-voting-rights-dd16294c-9cf3-4304-bbb9-04a31755f6fc.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-abortion-plan-voting-rights-dd16294c-9cf3-4304-bbb9-04a31755f6fc.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Proposed&lt;/a&gt; requiring states that restrict abortion access to clear new reproductive health laws with the DOJ.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sex work: &lt;/strong&gt;Supports &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;decriminalizing sex work&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/431610-kamala-harris-supports-decriminalizing-sex-work&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/431610-kamala-harris-supports-decriminalizing-sex-work&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;decriminalizing sex work&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Death penalty:&lt;/strong&gt; Proposes ending and has previously called for a &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;national moratorium&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2019/03/14/702707072/in-her-pitch-for-president-kamala-harris-focuses-on-criminal-justice-inequality&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2019/03/14/702707072/in-her-pitch-for-president-kamala-harris-focuses-on-criminal-justice-inequality&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;national moratorium&lt;/a&gt; on the death penalty.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Guns: &lt;/strong&gt;Proposed a &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;ban&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.politico.com/story/2019/05/15/kamala-harris-ban-imports-assault-weapons-1324581&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.politico.com/story/2019/05/15/kamala-harris-ban-imports-assault-weapons-1324581&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;ban&lt;/a&gt; on importing AR-15-style assault weapons. She has suggested executive orders requiring background checks, closing the &amp;quot;boyfriend&amp;quot; loophole and allowing victims to hold gun manufacturers responsible. She also supports mandatory buybacks on assault weapons.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HIV: &lt;/strong&gt;Would require private and public insurance plans to cover Pre-Exposure Prophylaxis (PrEP) without copays, along with any corresponding tests. The bill would include a grant program to increase access for uninsured Americans.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Income inequality: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Proposes investing&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-new-plan-invest-billions-black-homeowners-042aa516-03cc-40cb-947c-4b9b692fb892.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-new-plan-invest-billions-black-homeowners-042aa516-03cc-40cb-947c-4b9b692fb892.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Proposes investing&lt;/a&gt; $100 billion in black homeownership to close the racial inequality gap.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Domestic terrorism: &quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-domestic-terrorism-combat-plan-f8397b20-3529-428f-8384-b3653aa634dc.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-domestic-terrorism-combat-plan-f8397b20-3529-428f-8384-b3653aa634dc.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Domestic terrorism: &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Would create a federal &amp;quot;red flag&amp;quot; law and background checks.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Climate&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://kamalaharris.org/climate/&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://kamalaharris.org/climate/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Climate&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt; Wants a new &amp;quot;climate pollution fee&amp;quot; on industry, and to incorporate her &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;&amp;quot;climate equity act.&amp;quot;&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-generate-6a54b07d-e1c8-485d-b413-f2f88ec32d1a.html?chunk=1#story1&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-generate-6a54b07d-e1c8-485d-b413-f2f88ec32d1a.html?chunk=1#story1&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;climate equity act.&amp;quot;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criminal justice: &lt;/strong&gt;Proposed a plan to end mass incarceration, help felons reintegrate into society and increase oversight of police and prosecutors. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Childcare&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://kamalaharris.org/childrens-agenda/&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://kamalaharris.org/childrens-agenda/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Childcare&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt; Offered 6 months&amp;#x27; paid family leave, childcare subsidies and free preschool for low- and moderate-income families.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Student debt:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Proposes student loan&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/a29728977/kamala-harris-cosmopolitan-interview-equal-pay-marijuana/&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/a29728977/kamala-harris-cosmopolitan-interview-equal-pay-marijuana/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Proposes student loan&lt;/a&gt; forgiveness for those making less than $100,000 a year, free community college, making attending university debt-free and interest-free student loans.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Key criticisms:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Based on cases she &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;argued&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/17/opinion/kamala-harris-criminal-justice.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/17/opinion/kamala-harris-criminal-justice.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;argued&lt;/a&gt; and policies she enacted as California&amp;#x27;s attorney general:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;She defended the death penalty as attorney general, despite being personally against it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;She didn&amp;#x27;t take a position on Proposition 47, approved by voters, that reduced some felonies to misdemeanors.  &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Opposed a bill that would have required her office to investigate &lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;police shootings.&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/local/politics/la-me-pol-ca-harris-police-shootings-20160118-story.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-item=&quot;in_content_link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/local/politics/la-me-pol-ca-harris-police-shootings-20160118-story.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;police shootings.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h5&gt;1 fun thing:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;She is the first senator of Jamaican or Indian ancestry.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Go deeper: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;gtm-content-click&quot; data-vars-link-text=&quot;Everything you need to know about the other 2020 candidates&quot; data-vars-click-url=&quot;https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-candidate-profiles1552432119-facfee57-8089-4f14-bbdf-dc44ffa0ea4a.html&quot; data-vars-content-id=&quot;00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f&quot; data-vars-headline=&quot;Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words&quot; data-vars-event-category=&quot;story&quot; data-vars-sub-category=&quo