ayout></div><div class="sc-15x0qpo-0 iCOqgp"><amp-layout id="gtm-story" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-sub-category="story" class="i-amphtml-layout-container" i-amphtml-layout="container"><article class="sc-19m8jau-3 iHujCL grid-layout"><div class="sc-19m8jau-1 dEqaTd"><span class="time-rubric" data-testid="time-rubric"><span class="sc-31t5q3-8 eLNzOC sc-1g6idw6-0 gPPbsr">Updated Dec 3, 2019</span></span></div><div class="sc-19m8jau-0 hixqCw"><h1 class="sc-31t5q3-0 sc-1fjk95c-2 guveJc">Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words</h1><div class="sc-6usfji-0 lbJFqa"><div class="sc-6usfji-1 cpQxsz"><a title="Noa Yadidi" href="https://www.axios.com/authors/nyadidi"><div class="dm9ls1-0 bIqTEE"><amp-img src="https://images.axios.com/pzQ5FB8Xm9nNh_pmvQQEGCBOmcA=/877x149:4435x3707/52x0/2019/02/15/1550261663782.jpg" height="32" width="32" alt="Noa Yadidi" layout="responsive" data-testid="amp-tag" class="i-amphtml-layout-responsive i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="responsive"><i-amphtml-sizer style="display:block;padding-top:100.0000%;"></i-amphtml-sizer></amp-img></div></a></div><div class="sc-6usfji-3 iDBzbV"><a href="https://www.axios.com/authors/nyadidi">Noa Yadidi</a></div></div></div><div class="cbbc7v-0 iNrCiz"><div class="dm9ls1-0 bIqTEE"><amp-img src="https://images.axios.com/0wUUiRnQC2ypZJhJLuvfN82hAJ8=/0x274:3200x2074/1920x1080/2019/02/14/1550173034963.jpg" width="1920" height="1080" alt="Kamala Harris behind a podium at her campaign announcement" layout="responsive" data-testid="amp-tag" class="i-amphtml-layout-responsive i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="responsive"><i-amphtml-sizer style="display:block;padding-top:56.2500%;"></i-amphtml-sizer></amp-img></div><figcaption class="cbbc7v-1 gkungq"><p>Kamala Harris. Photo: Mason Trinca/Getty Images</p></figcaption></div><div class="sc-19m8jau-2 WfPNi"><div class="b0w77w-0 jctzOA gtm-story-text"><p><em><strong>Editor&#x27;s Note</strong>: Harris</em> <em><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="dropped out" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-drops-out-2020-campaign-50c45cbe-e917-4004-996c-1096b2a61a80.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-drops-out-2020-campaign-50c45cbe-e917-4004-996c-1096b2a61a80.html" target="_self">dropped out</a></em> <em>of the race on December 3rd, 2019. Below is our original article on her candidacy.</em></p><p>Democrat Kamala Harris is a California senator who took office at the start of Trump&#x27;s presidency and became one of the most vocal foils for Trump&#x27;s political nominees during heated questioning in confirmation hearings.</p><h5>Key facts:</h5><ul><li><strong>Current position: </strong>California senator — 2 years served</li><li><strong>Age: </strong>54</li><li><strong>Born: </strong>Oakland</li><li><strong>Undergraduate</strong>: Howard University</li><li><strong>Date candidacy announced: </strong>Jan. 21, 2019</li><li><strong>% of votes in line with Trump, </strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="per FiveThirtyEight" data-vars-click-url="https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/" target="_blank">per FiveThirtyEight</a>: 17.0%</li><li><strong>Previous roles: </strong>California attorney general (2011-2017); San Francisco district attorney (2004-2011); prosecutor</li></ul><h5>Stance on key issues:</h5><ul><li><strong>Green New Deal</strong>: <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Co-sponsor" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-green-new-deal-d0103689-3b72-4c6c-8018-cc8b18950476.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-green-new-deal-d0103689-3b72-4c6c-8018-cc8b18950476.html" target="_self">Co-sponsor</a></li><li><strong>Medicare for All</strong>: <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Co-sponsored Sen. Bernie Sanders" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-kamala-harris-medicare-for-all-d3598f7e-d492-4d45-9dc4-7a58c908556d.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/2020-presidential-election-kamala-harris-medicare-for-all-d3598f7e-d492-4d45-9dc4-7a58c908556d.html" target="_self">Co-sponsored Sen. Bernie Sanders</a>&#x27; bill.</li><li><strong>Drug prices:</strong> Would allow the Department of Health and Human Services to determine a &quot;fair price&quot; for drugs meeting certain conditions, per the <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Washington Post" data-vars-click-url="https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/kamala-harris-announces-plan-on-drug-prices-as-democratic-health-care-debate-intensifies/2019/07/15/a2d378a2-a731-11e9-9214-246e594de5d5_story.html?utm_term=.8cad6e7d6512" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/kamala-harris-announces-plan-on-drug-prices-as-democratic-health-care-debate-intensifies/2019/07/15/a2d378a2-a731-11e9-9214-246e594de5d5_story.html?utm_term=.8cad6e7d6512" target="_blank">Washington Post</a>.</li><li><strong>Marijuana legalization: </strong>Proposed<a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text=" federal legalization of marijuana" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-marijuana-2020-presidential-election-746539ba-edad-457f-8790-16675d628d9f.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-marijuana-2020-presidential-election-746539ba-edad-457f-8790-16675d628d9f.html" target="_self"> federal legalization of marijuana</a>.</li><li><strong>Teacher pay: </strong>Has<a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text=" a plan to give the average teacher a $13,500 salary increase" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-teacher-pay-plan-7d7cc1e6-a157-4f5a-9117-8a6b60e3f8b8.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-teacher-pay-plan-7d7cc1e6-a157-4f5a-9117-8a6b60e3f8b8.html" target="_self"> a plan to give the average teacher a $13,500 salary increase</a>, costing an estimated $315 billion over 10 years.</li><li><strong>Taxes: </strong>Introduced the LIFT the Middle Class Act, which <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Vox&#x27;s Dylan Matthews explained" data-vars-click-url="https://www.vox.com/future-perfect/2018/10/19/17995374/kamala-harris-lift-act-basic-income-cash-eitc" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.vox.com/future-perfect/2018/10/19/17995374/kamala-harris-lift-act-basic-income-cash-eitc" target="_blank">Vox&#x27;s Dylan Matthews explained</a> as an expansion of the earned income tax credit. She also proposed offering tax credits to help people pay rent.</li><ul><li>In May, said she&#x27;d <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="fully repeal the 2017 Republican tax law" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-trump-tax-law-lift-act-b6cd009c-5ce2-42de-8d3d-4b62289531c8.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-trump-tax-law-lift-act-b6cd009c-5ce2-42de-8d3d-4b62289531c8.html" target="_self">fully repeal the 2017 Republican tax law</a> and replace it with LIFT.</li></ul><li><strong>Abortion: </strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Proposed" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-abortion-plan-voting-rights-dd16294c-9cf3-4304-bbb9-04a31755f6fc.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-abortion-plan-voting-rights-dd16294c-9cf3-4304-bbb9-04a31755f6fc.html" target="_self">Proposed</a> requiring states that restrict abortion access to clear new reproductive health laws with the DOJ.</li><li><strong>Sex work: </strong>Supports <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="decriminalizing sex work" data-vars-click-url="https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/431610-kamala-harris-supports-decriminalizing-sex-work" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/431610-kamala-harris-supports-decriminalizing-sex-work" target="_blank">decriminalizing sex work</a>.</li><li><strong>Death penalty:</strong> Proposes ending and has previously called for a <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="national moratorium" data-vars-click-url="https://www.npr.org/2019/03/14/702707072/in-her-pitch-for-president-kamala-harris-focuses-on-criminal-justice-inequality" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.npr.org/2019/03/14/702707072/in-her-pitch-for-president-kamala-harris-focuses-on-criminal-justice-inequality" target="_blank">national moratorium</a> on the death penalty.</li><li><strong>Guns: </strong>Proposed a <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="ban" data-vars-click-url="https://www.politico.com/story/2019/05/15/kamala-harris-ban-imports-assault-weapons-1324581" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.politico.com/story/2019/05/15/kamala-harris-ban-imports-assault-weapons-1324581" target="_blank">ban</a> on importing AR-15-style assault weapons. She has suggested executive orders requiring background checks, closing the &quot;boyfriend&quot; loophole and allowing victims to hold gun manufacturers responsible. She also supports mandatory buybacks on assault weapons.</li><li><strong>HIV: </strong>Would require private and public insurance plans to cover Pre-Exposure Prophylaxis (PrEP) without copays, along with any corresponding tests. The bill would include a grant program to increase access for uninsured Americans.</li><li><strong>Income inequality: </strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Proposes investing" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-new-plan-invest-billions-black-homeowners-042aa516-03cc-40cb-947c-4b9b692fb892.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-new-plan-invest-billions-black-homeowners-042aa516-03cc-40cb-947c-4b9b692fb892.html" target="_self">Proposes investing</a> $100 billion in black homeownership to close the racial inequality gap.</li><li><strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Domestic terrorism: " data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-domestic-terrorism-combat-plan-f8397b20-3529-428f-8384-b3653aa634dc.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/kamala-harris-domestic-terrorism-combat-plan-f8397b20-3529-428f-8384-b3653aa634dc.html" target="_self">Domestic terrorism: </a></strong>Would create a federal &quot;red flag&quot; law and background checks.</li><li><strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Climate" data-vars-click-url="https://kamalaharris.org/climate/" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://kamalaharris.org/climate/" target="_blank">Climate</a>:</strong> Wants a new &quot;climate pollution fee&quot; on industry, and to incorporate her <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="&quot;climate equity act.&quot;" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-generate-6a54b07d-e1c8-485d-b413-f2f88ec32d1a.html?chunk=1#story1" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-generate-6a54b07d-e1c8-485d-b413-f2f88ec32d1a.html?chunk=1#story1" target="_self">&quot;climate equity act.&quot;</a></li><li><strong>Criminal justice: </strong>Proposed a plan to end mass incarceration, help felons reintegrate into society and increase oversight of police and prosecutors. </li><li><strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Childcare" data-vars-click-url="https://kamalaharris.org/childrens-agenda/" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://kamalaharris.org/childrens-agenda/" target="_blank">Childcare</a>:</strong> Offered 6 months&#x27; paid family leave, childcare subsidies and free preschool for low- and moderate-income families.</li><li><strong>Student debt:</strong> <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Proposes student loan" data-vars-click-url="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/a29728977/kamala-harris-cosmopolitan-interview-equal-pay-marijuana/" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/politics/a29728977/kamala-harris-cosmopolitan-interview-equal-pay-marijuana/" target="_blank">Proposes student loan</a> forgiveness for those making less than $100,000 a year, free community college, making attending university debt-free and interest-free student loans.</li></ul><h5>Key criticisms:</h5><ul><li>Based on cases she <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="argued" data-vars-click-url="https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/17/opinion/kamala-harris-criminal-justice.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/17/opinion/kamala-harris-criminal-justice.html" target="_blank">argued</a> and policies she enacted as California&#x27;s attorney general:</li><ul><li>She defended the death penalty as attorney general, despite being personally against it.</li><li>She didn&#x27;t take a position on Proposition 47, approved by voters, that reduced some felonies to misdemeanors. </li><li>Opposed a bill that would have required her office to investigate <a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="police shootings." data-vars-click-url="https://www.latimes.com/local/politics/la-me-pol-ca-harris-police-shootings-20160118-story.html" data-vars-content-id="00a60a29-6560-4746-ab68-a4c508554a1f" data-vars-headline="Kamala Harris on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="story" data-vars-sub-category="story" data-vars-item="in_content_link" href="https://www.latimes.com/local/politics/la-me-pol-ca-harris-police-shootings-20160118-story.html" target="_blank">police shootings.</a></li></ul></ul><h5>1 fun thing:</h5><ul><li>She is the first senator of Jamaican or Indian ancestry.</li></ul><p><strong>Go deeper: </strong><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-link-text="Everything you need to know about the other 2020 candidates" data-vars-click-url=