"sc-1jy24uc-7 lmFuci content-card grid-layout"><div class="sc-6usfji-0 sc-1jy24uc-4 fPAeYR"><div class="sc-6usfji-1 cpQxsz"><a title="Axios" href="https://www.axios.com/authors/newsdesk"><div class="dm9ls1-0 bIqTEE"><amp-img src="https://static.axios.com/img/axios-icon.png" height="32" width="32" alt="Axios" layout="responsive" data-testid="amp-tag" class="i-amphtml-layout-responsive i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="responsive"><i-amphtml-sizer style="display:block;padding-top:100.0000%;"></i-amphtml-sizer></amp-img></div></a></div><div class="sc-6usfji-3 iDBzbV"><a href="https://www.axios.com/authors/fallassan">Fadel Allassan</a><span>, </span><a href="https://www.axios.com/authors/uperano">Ursula Perano</a></div></div><h3 class="sc-31t5q3-2 sc-1fjk95c-0 sc-1jy24uc-5 clcUiY"><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-content-id="87601306-f580-4d77-9f0c-77fcb5351a04" data-vars-link-text="Michael Bloomberg on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-headline="Michael Bloomberg on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="recirc" data-vars-index="1" data-vars-item="headline" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/michael-bloomberg-factsheet-2020-president-democrat-87601306-f580-4d77-9f0c-77fcb5351a04.html" data-vars-sub-category="atomic_unit_full" href="https://www.axios.com/michael-bloomberg-factsheet-2020-president-democrat-87601306-f580-4d77-9f0c-77fcb5351a04.html">Michael Bloomberg on the issues, in under 500 words</a></h3><figure data-testid="au-image" class="sc-1jy24uc-2 bUgOWv"><a class="gtm-content-click" data-vars-content-id="87601306-f580-4d77-9f0c-77fcb5351a04" data-vars-link-text="Michael Bloomberg on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-headline="Michael Bloomberg on the issues, in under 500 words" data-vars-event-category="recirc" data-vars-index="1" data-vars-item="featured_image" data-vars-sub-category="atomic_unit_full" data-vars-click-url="https://www.axios.com/michael-bloomberg-factsheet-2020-president-democrat-